@startmindmap
* Money as coins (eUTXO)
** Two ways to keep money
*** Bank balance (one big number)
*** Jar of real coins (Cardano's way)
** How a coin is spent
*** You hand over whole coins
*** You get change back as a new coin
*** Coins in equals coins out plus fee
*** A coin can be spent only once
** Bitcoin's treasure chest
*** A coin and a simple lock
*** The guard sees almost nothing
** What Cardano adds
*** Sticky note on the chest (Datum)
*** The note you hand over (Redeemer)
*** Guard reads the whole receipt (Context)
** The guard is a referee
*** Only says yes or no
*** Never grabs or sends money
** Why it is nice
*** You know the answer before you go
*** Other tokens ride in the same chest
@endmindmap
